Package: tealeaves
Version: 0.0.3
Date: 2018-11-13
Title: Solve for leaf temperature using energy balance
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Muir", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "cdmuir@hawaii.edu")
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), units (>= 0.6.0)
Imports: crayon (>= 1.3.0),
         dplyr (>= 0.7.0),
         glue (>= 1.3.0),
